column2: "Ahoy Matey! Whar's that spicy lass ye were wit' last?"
"I wonder what else you have to say when I'm not around, huh?"
"Well aren't ye in a jolly mood this day. Usually ye'd have taken a swin' at me!"
"Haven't seen ye in a while, 'n ye changed yer look, eh? Wha's wit' the uniform?"
"Oh, this? Ever since Zeno came home, I realized I was pushing myself to be something I'm not."
"Hunter was fun and all, but Force suits me the best."
"It suits ye fine... well, 'cept fer one thin' it be missin'..."
"Somethin' that embodies ye wild side, t'warn onlookers th' kraken come'th!"
"Shiver me timbers! Almost met me maker!"
"Ye ain't turn a new leaf at all!! Ye be even more dangerous then a'fore!"
"Wit' ye lover back on deck, inn'it time ye act like a proper lass?"
"You can now call Echo (EP3) as a partner."
